---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="About TheEduAssist" description="Learn about TheEduAssist, what we build, and why clients choose us for their learning solutions.">

        <section class="py-20 bg-slate-100 text-center px-4">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">About TheEduAssist</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">Professional, practical, and outcome-focused learning solutions.</p>
            <a href="/book-free-audit/" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-blue-700">Book Free Audit</a>
        </section>

        <section class="py-20 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 space-y-12">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">TheEduAssist is a dedicated team of learning professionals, instructional designers, and technical experts. We serve clients remotely, providing reliable support for eLearning and platform management.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">What We Help Clients Build</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">We help turn raw content and ideas into structured, engaging online learning experiences. From full custom course design to setting up robust LMS platforms and Kajabi ecosystems, we handle the technical and pedagogical heavy lifting.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Why Clients Work With Us</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Clients choose us for our practical delivery approach. We do not use generic AI jargon, make exaggerated claims, or promise fake results. We deliver clear, outcome-focused solutions tailored to actual learner needs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

</Layout>
